wikipedia_page.main: George Hugh Boscawen, 9th Viscount Falmouth,  (born 31 October 1919), is a British peer and landowner. His subsidiary titles include Baron Le Despencer (created 1264) and Baron Boscawen-Rose. A former officer in the Coldstream Guards, he was Lord Lieutenant of Cornwall from 1977 to 1994.
